  @fn nearestStop(mouseX, mouseY)  @ 795-810
      @contract  returns (col, stop, fracX) or (nil, nil, fracX)
      @invariant  fracX is separate so callers distinguish 'past last col' from 'inside col N'
  @fn add(key, byte)  @ 816

